  "description": "<p><strong>JOIN US TODAY</strong></p><p>VA Organization is a leading sales and marketing organisation based in Singapore. We help our clients to generate high revenues and forging strong brand awareness to the public. We are currently looking for driven individuals to join our expanding team!</p><p><strong>SCOPE</strong></p><ul><li>Manage team and sales initiatives to achieve client objectives.</li><li>Oversee the performance of marketing events and outreach efforts.</li><li>Evaluate the effectiveness of strategies based on campaign goals.</li><li>Provide overall support to the team and facilitate growth.</li></ul><p><strong>BENEFITS</strong></p><ul><li>Career progression </li><li>Travelling opportunities </li><li>Fun, supportive environment</li><li>1 to 1 mentorship</li></ul><p><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Business mindset, driven to be part of an excelling team</li><li>Process driven, willingness to contribute</li><li>Self-motivated character</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to join a leading organisation in Asia, apply now and enquire more to kickstart your career!</strong></p>",
